  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Escape the zombie infected zone, using an arsenal of weapons, in this arena shooter game.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Due to a malfunction you crash landed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And now you are stuck behind an apocalyptic infection zone, crawling with zombies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The headquarter will provide directions on how to escape this danger zone, so stay on your toes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way through the endless horde of the living dead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will have an arsenal of weapons you will find in the post apocalyptic region.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way to the safe zone, if you can. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay features arena shooter weapon system, Go and Gib!!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Escape the zombie infected zone, using an arsenal of weapons, in this arena shooter game.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Due to a malfunction you crash landed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And now you are stuck behind an apocalyptic infection zone, crawling with zombies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The headquarter will provide directions on how to escape this danger zone, so stay on your toes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way through the endless horde of the living dead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will have an arsenal of weapons you will find in the post apocalyptic region.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way to the safe zone, if you can. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay features arena shooter weapon system, Go and Gib!!</p>",
